message.body: I'm glad we went out yesterday because right now, I hate this.
I'm glad we did too. And I'm sorry you have to put up with work today. We'll have nice weather again someday.
Awww thanks, that's touching. Really, that leaked me feel better :) I'm just going with it. Are you out with everyone? Would you mind telling then about Zombie Saturday?
I'm not with everyone. Me and Eden are waiting for the concert. Are you free tomorrow? We're thinking about meeting for lunch
So you're not meeting up with Jenny and Sam today?
We're meeting them for lunch tomorrow around 1.
